data.answer: The photo shows that there is a girl looking at an animal that is crawling on her arm. It is a mantis on her arm. She is wearing a pink shirt and she has blonde hair. She is opening up her mouth when she is observing the mantis. There are some trees and flowers in the background of the image. I think she is in an outdoor environment.
